HEADWORD: Blunger
<hw>Blun"ger</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Corrupted from
<ets>plunger</ets>.]</ety> <def>A wooden blade with a cross handle, used
for mixing the clay in potteries; a plunger.</def>
<rj><au>Tomlinson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
